cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SY

The paper proposes a new optimization method for neural networks, which is a common topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also uses stochastic gradient descent, which is a common optimization algorithm in machine learning (cs.AI). The experiments are conducted on image classification tasks, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). Finally, the paper analyzes the algorithm using the Fokker-Planck formalism, which is a common tool in control theory and stochastic systems (cs.SY).
